    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "That is definitely not going to happen. gRPC needs to build from sources out of the box for Ruby, Python, etc. The only required dependency on native extension packages for these languages is only a C compiler.\r\n\r\nDoing this kind of change would make it impossible for these source packages to build properly out of the box on anyone's machine."
